 07 17<br>
key2=3Dff 42 9d 00 c4 d6 1f fc 2f 1f 2e 52 a2 95 00 00<br>
<br>
<b>Step 3: Hash Check</b><br>
This step extracts a 10 bit hash from bytes 13, 14, and 15. Then it compute=
s a hash with the help of a lookup table and compares them.<br>
